│ pre-widened source type (`InputTypeA`) and the kind of extension (`ExtAType`) using the    │
│ correct `TTI::CastContextHint` enum members: `Signed` and `Unsigned`.                      │
│                                                                                            │
│ This ensures the cost model has complete and accurate information, allowing it to          │
│ correctly calculate costs, which fixes the crash and prevents the vectorizer from making   │
│ suboptimal choices. All tests have passed with this patch.                                 │
